ield strength is characterized by fit parameters that\nseem to show convergence for larger values of the magnetic Reynolds number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 19:29:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-10-30"}
