arly important considering the recent interest in the\nspectra of the electromagnetic counterparts of events producing gravitational\nwaves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 20:56:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2011 20:06:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Dec 2012 03:24:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-24"}
