the dependence\nof the critical time $T^{\\ast}$ on the coupling strength between qubits and the\ntarget gate transformation. Practical consequences of these findings for\nlaboratory implementation of quantum gates are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2011 21:27:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2012 17:46:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 2 Dec 2012 01:54:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-01"}
