eriment. This is also the\nessential and non-trivial difference with the \\Gamma=1 sample, where the\nvertically-aligned vortices are distributed randomly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2011 09:45:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2012 13:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Jun 2012 23:14:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2012 17:25:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-26"}
